00:00:03,020 --> 00:00:04,650
You are being watched.

3
00:00:05,440 --> 00:00:07,770
The government has a secret system-

4
00:00:07,770 --> 00:00:11,700
a machine that spies on you every hour of every day.

5
00:00:12,270 --> 00:00:16,300
I designed the machine to detect acts of terror, but it sees everything...

6
00:00:16,300 --> 00:00:19,270
Violent crimes involving ordinary people.

7
00:00:19,820 --> 00:00:22,520
The government considers these people irrelevant.

8
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:23,860
We don't.

9
00:00:24,950 --> 00:00:29,020
Hunted by the authorities, we work in secret.

10
00:00:29,400 --> 00:00:30,980
You will never find us.

11
00:00:31,250 --> 00:00:33,440
But victim or perpetrator,

12
