499
00:39:57,520 --> 00:40:00,290
Glad to be back. I'll see you soon.

500
00:40:02,240 --> 00:40:06,560
Chip off the old block, huh? Looks like he's doing okay.

501
00:40:07,120 --> 00:40:09,330
You, on the other hand, look like crap.

502
00:40:11,770 --> 00:40:12,870
Heard you took a bullet.

503
00:40:12,870 --> 00:40:15,790
Yeah, stupid bastard shot me where I had plenty of padding.

504
00:40:15,790 --> 00:40:17,370
Would've gone for the head shot myself.

505
00:40:17,370 --> 00:40:19,700
Course, you got plenty of padding there too.

506
00:40:19,700 --> 00:40:21,350
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

507
00:40:28,140 --> 00:40:30,930
Thank you, truly.

508
00:40:31,990 --> 00:40:33,800
Shut up and drive, Lionel.

509
00:40:50,060 --> 00:40:53,800
