511
00:40:58,450 --> 00:40:59,680
So...

512
00:41:01,130 --> 00:41:02,750
am I in trouble?

513
00:41:07,770 --> 00:41:11,430
Got your man locked up, Carter. Must feel good.

514
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:12,690
Not all of them.

515
00:41:12,690 --> 00:41:15,540
Still haven't been able to locate our pal Simmons.

516
00:41:16,110 --> 00:41:18,040
