517
00:41:20,310 --> 00:41:24,720
All right, where's my weapon? John Doe didn't have a permit.

518
00:41:25,990 --> 00:41:28,910
Your gun's property of the NYPD now.

519
00:41:29,120 --> 00:41:33,770
Time I got some new hardware. Looks like your ride is here.

520
00:41:36,020 --> 00:41:38,390
Guess we were all worried about you.

521
00:41:40,950 --> 00:41:42,690
If my number was up,

522
00:41:43,560 --> 00:41:45,700
I'm just glad I was with you.

523
00:41:52,570 --> 00:41:55,160
No one I'd rather be with at the end.

524
00:41:56,990 --> 00:42:00,220
<i>Your time's up.</i> Told you I'd end you.

525
00:42:01,250 --> 00:42:03,480
No, not today!

526
00:42:09,980 --> 00:42:14,270
Joss, Joss, I'm here.

527
00:42:18,710 --> 00:42:19,880
It's okay.

528
00:42:20,630 --> 00:42:22,740
I need- I need to see my boy.

529
00:42:23,830 --> 00:42:26,650
I need to tell him- And you will, and you will.

530
00:42:26,650 --> 00:42:28,170
Just stay with me.

531
00:42:32,800 --> 00:42:36,030
Promise me you'll look in on him.

532
00:42:37,290 --> 00:42:39,000
I won't have to 'cause you're gonna make it, okay?

533
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:40,980
Promise me you'll tell him.

534
